sequenceDiagram
    actor User as "사용자"
    participant TopicPage as "topics/[id]/page.tsx"
    participant MatchPage as "matches/[id]/page.tsx"
    participant Viewer as "DebateViewer.tsx"
    participant Stream as "useDebateStream.ts"
    participant Store as "debateStore.ts"
    participant Proxy as "api/[...path]/route.ts"
    participant TopicAPI as "debate_topics.py"
    participant MatchSvc as "debate/matching_service.py"
    participant Engine as "debate/engine.py"
    participant Orch as "debate/orchestrator.py"
    participant Broadcast as "debate/broadcast.py"

    User->>TopicPage: 토픽 선택 및 에이전트 선택
    User->>TopicPage: 큐 등록 버튼 클릭
    TopicPage->>Proxy: POST /api/topics/{id}/queue
    Proxy->>TopicAPI: join_queue()
    TopicAPI->>MatchSvc: DebateAutoMatcher 감지
    MatchSvc->>MatchSvc: ready_up() - DebateMatch 생성
    MatchSvc->>Engine: run_debate() 백그라운드 실행

    User->>MatchPage: 매치 뷰어 페이지 진입
    MatchPage->>Viewer: mount - match props 전달
    Viewer->>Stream: useDebateStream(matchId, status) 호출
    Viewer->>Store: fetchTurns(matchId)
    Stream->>Proxy: GET /api/matches/{id}/stream
    Proxy->>Broadcast: subscribe(match_channel)

    loop 턴 루프 (N 라운드)
        Engine->>Orch: review_turn() - asyncio.gather()
        Orch->>Broadcast: publish_event(turn_chunk)
        Broadcast->>Proxy: Redis Pub/Sub 메시지
        Proxy->>Stream: SSE data: turn_chunk
        Stream->>Store: appendChunk(turn_number, speaker, chunk)
        Store->>Viewer: streamingTurn 상태 업데이트
        Viewer->>User: StreamingTurnBubble - 실시간 청크 표시

        Orch->>Broadcast: publish_event(turn)
        Broadcast->>Proxy: Redis Pub/Sub 메시지
        Proxy->>Stream: SSE data: turn
        Stream->>Store: addTurnFromSSE(turnLog)
        Store->>Viewer: turns 배열 업데이트
        Viewer->>User: TurnBubble - 완료 턴 + 검토 결과 표시

        Orch->>Broadcast: publish_event(turn_review)
        Stream->>Store: addTurnReview(review)
    end

    Engine->>Broadcast: publish_event(finished)
    Broadcast->>Proxy: Redis Pub/Sub 메시지
    Proxy->>Stream: SSE data: finished
    Stream->>Store: setDebateShowAll(true) + fetchMatch()
    Store->>Viewer: match 최종 상태 반영
    Viewer->>User: 결과 표시 - ELO 변동 / 승자
    User->>Viewer: 리플레이 버튼 클릭
    Viewer->>Viewer: startReplay() - useDebateReplay tick
    Viewer->>User: ReplayControls + TurnBubble 순차 재생
